<div class="title">The Adderall Did Something</div>
<div class="substance">Mushrooms - P. cubensis & Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Saribo&Exact=1">Saribo</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Saribo. "The Adderall Did Something: An Experience with Mushrooms - P. cubensis & Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp26865)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 2, 2007. erowid.org/exp/26865</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

